<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>About Us - Naye Pankh Foundation</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>

<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<section class="about">

    <h1><span class="sticker">🌿</span>About Naye Pankh Foundation</h1>

    <p>
        Naye Pankh Foundation is a non-profit organization dedicated to
        creating positive change in society through education, community
        development, health awareness, and youth empowerment.
    </p>

    <p>
        We believe that every individual deserves equal opportunities
        to learn, grow, and achieve their dreams. Through our various
        initiatives and volunteer-driven activities, we strive to make
        a meaningful impact in the lives of children, women, and
        underprivileged communities.
    </p>

    <br>

    <h2><span class="sticker">🎯</span>Our Mission</h2>

    <p>
        To empower communities by providing access to education,
        healthcare awareness, skill development, and social support.
    </p>

    <br>

    <h2><span class="sticker">✨</span>Our Vision</h2>

    <p>
        To build a society where every individual has the opportunity
        to live with dignity, confidence, and hope for a better future.
    </p>

    <br>

    <h2><span class="sticker">💛</span>Our Core Values</h2>

    <ul>
        <li>Education for All</li>
        <li>Community Service</li>
        <li>Transparency & Trust</li>
        <li>Empowerment & Equality</li>
        <li>Compassion & Humanity</li>
    </ul>

    <br>

    <h2><span class="sticker">📊</span>Our Impact</h2>

    <div class="impact-container">

        <div class="impact-box">
            <h3>500+</h3>
            <p>🤝 Volunteers</p>
        </div>

        <div class="impact-box">
            <h3>1000+</h3>
            <p>✨ Lives Impacted</p>
        </div>

        <div class="impact-box">
            <h3>50+</h3>
            <p>📅 Events Conducted</p>
        </div>

    </div>

</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>

</body>
</html>
